---
title: Date field
---
The `date` field stores a Date string, collected from an `<input type="date">` form field.

## Usage example

```typescript
date: fields.date({
  label: 'Event date',
  description: 'The date of the event'
})
```

## Type signature

```typescript
date({
  label: string;
  defaultValue?: string | {
    kind: 'today';
  };
  validation?: {
    isRequired?: IsRequired;
    min?: string;
    max?: string;
  };
  description?: string;
})
```
